                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-86-off401 t17850223-86-cd402"></join>, one watch, with the inside case made of gold, and the outside case made of shagreen, value 8 l. one steel chain, value 1 s. one cornelian seal set in gold, value 5 s. one gold acorn, value 1 s. one silver watch, value 20 s. one stone seal set in base metal, value 6 d. and one base metal key, value 3 d. the property of 
                     
